<h1>越南战争结束50年后，炸弹仍造成人员伤亡</h1>
<p>Author: 半岛电视台</p>
<p>Publisher: Al Jazeera</p>
<p>Published Time: 2023-06-26T03:28:08</p>
<p>Modified Time: 2023-06-26T03:56:53</p>
<p>Description: 美国已投入数百万美元清理未爆炸弹药，但农民和儿童仍不断发现未爆炸的导弹。</p>
<p>Images: ["<a href="https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-1687746937.jpg">1-1687746937.jpg</a>", "<a href="https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2-1687746944.jpg">2-1687746944.jpg</a>", "<a href="https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/3-1687746951.jpg">3-1687746951.jpg</a>", "<a href="https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/4-1687746957.jpg">4-1687746957.jpg</a>", "<a href="https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/5-1687746963.jpg">5-1687746963.jpg</a>"]</p>
